IMAPAccount gmail
Host imap.gmail.com
User a3madkour@gmail.com
PassCmd "pass Email/Google | head -n 1"
SSLType IMAPS
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt

IMAPStore gmail-remote
Account gmail

MaildirStore gmail-local
SubFolders Verbatim
Path ~/.mail/gmail/
Inbox ~/.mail/gmail/Inbox
Trash ~/.mail/gmail/Trash

Channel gmail
Far :gmail-remote:
Near :gmail-local:
Patterns *
SyncState *
Create Both
Expunge Both
CopyArrivalDate yes
Sync All

IMAPAccount work
Host localhost
User madkour.a@northeastern.edu
PassCmd "pass neu.edu/prod-web.neu.edu | head -n 1"
port 1143
SSLType None
AuthMechs LOGIN
# Increase timeout to avoid o365 IMAP hiccups
Timeout 120
PipelineDepth 50

IMAPStore work-remote
Account work

MaildirStore work-local
# Note the trailing slash on the Path statement!
Path ~/.mail/work/
Inbox ~/.mail/work/Inbox
SubFolders Verbatim

Channel work
Far :work-remote:
Near :work-local:
#Include everything
Patterns *
# Sync changes (creations/deletions) with the server
Create Both
# Expunge Both
SyncState *
